[b]Introduction:[/b] [i]Hello Moparscape. You might be asking yourself, what the fuck is this? Well, I don't really have an answer for you. The concept for this server was made up on the spot. It is all based on 'Ovaries.' I have spent countless hours on this project, and hope you enjoy.[/i]
[b]Media:[/b] [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2ij3n9g.png[/img] <---- OMG! Ovaries as a logout button? [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/20jn3ty.png[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/n4eg04.png[/img] [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/262mj9g.png[/img]
Credits: Mr Dope Allstar Whoever else
[b]Note:[/b] No, but seriously, my next release will be alot more serious, I have had alot of stress in my life the past couple days, and I just needed a laugh.
[b]Thanks to[/b]: Daginith, SilentCJ, lilxCJ, and Mr Dope!
